@startuml Search and Accept Flow - Current

title ProspectOS Web - Search and Accept Lead Flow

actor User as U
participant "SearchPage" as SP
participant "Lead API" as API

U -> SP: Open /search
SP -> API: GET /api/icps
API --> SP: ICP list

U -> SP: Fill query + limit + optional icpId
U -> SP: Click "Buscar prospects"
SP -> API: POST /api/leads/search
API --> SP: LeadSearchResponse

alt Search error
    SP --> U: Show ErrorState + Retry
else Search success
    SP --> U: Show leads in DataTable
    U -> SP: Click "Aceitar"
    SP -> API: POST /api/leads/accept
    API --> SP: AcceptLeadResponse (company)
    SP -> SP: invalidateQueries(["companies"])
    SP --> U: Show feedback + link /companies/{id}
end

@enduml
